Reasoning: The paper proposes an end-to-end deep learning model for predicting future risk from Electronic Medical Records. The model uses a combination of techniques from natural language processing, set theory, and recurrent neural networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper deals with healthcare data, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
